Description: Hitachi Bonded Abrasives are made with a patented multi-layer contruction. Top layer of glass fiber protects the worker agains chipping off of abrasive grains. The V28 LITHIUM-ION battery pack offers up to twice the run-time of an 18V NiCd or NiMH pack and is actually lighter than 18V NiCd and NiMH packs! LITHIUM-ION technology allows consistent fade-free power - meaning the first cut is as powerful as the last. V28 LITHIUM-ION battery packs will never develop a memory and can be charged at any time regardless of the pack's current charge level!
